Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.84,0:02:56.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小咲又是正負0點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.88,0:02:59.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算上昨天的已經連續四回了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.48,0:03:00.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可思議喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.65,0:03:04.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宮永同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.77,0:03:05.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.40,0:03:08.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻將是以勝利為目標的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.72,0:03:10.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.95,0:03:14.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次請為了贏而打麻將
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.05,0:03:25.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.27,0:03:28.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我知道了」？！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.56,0:03:32.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說能確定贏我們嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.06,0:03:40.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「贏」就是指拿第一對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.92,0:03:42.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.94,0:03:46.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正負0點的話  是成不了第一的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.61,0:03:54.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…就當自己的初始點是1000點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.11,0:03:57.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別人的初始點是33000點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.82,0:03:59.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼想如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.64,0:04:00.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.72,0:04:01.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.11,0:04:04.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咲是1000點…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.63,0:04:14.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不就相當於開始就給了其他三人每人8000點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.26,0:04:26.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這樣的點數打成正負0點…就能贏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.93,0:04:28.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來很難啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.83,0:04:31.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.82,0:04:46.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宮永同學到現在為止連續四回正負0點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.11,0:04:50.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  調整點數與贏所需的技術是不一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.18,0:04:54.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能確定贏…是不可能的事喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.47,0:05:02.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立直
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.69,0:05:04.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙重立直？！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.09,0:05:05.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.23,0:05:16.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙重立直一發自摸  閒家2000點  莊家3900點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.82,0:05:20.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這不是我的得意技嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.43,0:05:22.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你出千了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.10,0:05:24.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是全自動麻將桌啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.53,0:05:28.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從前一局開始就持續強運呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.87,0:05:30.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種只不過是一時運氣好而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.22,0:05:32.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,單純的偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.87,0:05:41.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.14,0:05:43.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,點和
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.59,0:05:46.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7700點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.90,0:05:53.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立直
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.76,0:05:56.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.18,0:05:58.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小和來勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.76,0:06:04.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自摸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.86,0:06:06.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立直平和一發自摸加一赤牌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.55,0:06:08.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每人4000點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.95,0:06:11.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用我的這局莊家來贏你！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.22,0:06:19.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和才過一會兒就勢頭這麼好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.45,0:06:21.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於發揮出原來的實力了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.55,0:06:35.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去的話  我的得意技就被一直奪去了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.82,0:06:43.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行就立直
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.89,0:06:45.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會讓你得逞的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.59,0:06:51.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,11600點在一本場是11900點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.64,0:06:54.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就交給和了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.62,0:06:57.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下點數差就變成了33400點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.13,0:07:00.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把她遠遠拋在身後了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.88,0:07:31.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.86,0:07:41.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,點和
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.22,0:07:44.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,6400點在二本場就是7000點喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.24,0:07:46.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於和了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.75,0:07:52.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連小和也沒看破我的暗聽七對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.01,0:07:55.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  這次就是最後一局了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.58,0:08:07.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宮永同學一開始和過之後就這樣一直輸嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.43,0:08:12.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我與宮永同學的點數差是26400點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.70,0:08:17.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算跳滿的直擊也無法動搖我的第一
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.80,0:08:21.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小零的自摸好運也到此為止了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.57,0:08:25.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算滿貫加了8000點也還是負1000點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.26,0:08:27.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是成不了正負0點的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.43,0:08:31.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要某人不立直的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.15,0:08:33.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立直
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.85,0:08:35.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然立直啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.84,0:08:45.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能有意識地以實力打出正負0點的話  也應該能有意識地贏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.22,0:08:50.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有種不可思議的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.01,0:08:55.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今為止我打麻將時都不曾有過這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.07,0:08:57.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種感覺是什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.93,0:09:02.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…在想著去贏！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.31,0:09:07.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果  她真的身有強運的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.47,0:09:14.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果  不知道贏的壓力的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.80,0:09:21.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天  我和了也沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.55,0:09:24.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,槓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.69,0:09:26.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又槓西風？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.54,0:09:28.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  難不成…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.64,0:09:32.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.92,0:09:39.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.27,0:09:47.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自摸  四暗刻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.65,0:09:53.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,役…役…役滿？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.11,0:09:57.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且又是嶺上開花
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.36,0:10:02.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,役滿32000點…加立直棒不就33000點了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.81,0:10:08.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她真的把33000點的負點變成了0點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.40,0:10:13.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.21,0:10:18.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.28,0:10:20.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.02,0:10:24.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,====================================
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.13,0:10:30.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.13,0:10:36.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…還是第一次打出役滿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.86,0:10:41.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今為止就算有機會我也拆牌了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.12,0:10:48.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終局了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.63,0:10:59.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  要贏還真是難啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.84,0:11:02.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又成了正負0點了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.74,0:11:07.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  小咲你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.95,0:11:11.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這次不也是原村同學大獲全勝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.57,0:11:15.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是初始點1000點  所以是第二名啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.55,0:11:18.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,點數結果是這樣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.60,0:11:26.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然  一直以為是那個點數  才會役滿的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.08,0:11:28.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宮永同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.26,0:11:31.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我是說了「當成1000點」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.99,0:11:35.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上還是全員初始點25000點  和普通一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.61,0:11:39.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際的點數是這樣的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.00,0:11:48.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小咲是21200點加上立直棒的1000點與四暗刻的32000點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.94,0:11:50.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總共54200點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.88,0:11:53.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正44的第一名啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.70,0:11:55.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.17,0:11:57.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.19,0:11:58.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贏了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.82,0:12:00.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我贏了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.07,0:12:02.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咲也是有優點的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.29,0:12:06.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且又想打成正負0點…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.43,0:12:08.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小咲好厲害喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.66,0:12:10.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  你做得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.41,0:12:13.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贏了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.52,0:12:18.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.22,0:12:22.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贏了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.90,0:12:28.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小和？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.14,0:12:32.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來？！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.95,0:12:47.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小和好像在哭…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.55,0:12:48.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不至於吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.05,0:13:04.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  宮永同學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.75,0:13:07.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約定的書在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.72,0:13:11.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是在待局時打發時間用的讀書書櫃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.56,0:13:14.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進麻將部的話就隨你讀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.62,0:13:20.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在意和嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.02,0:13:24.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,書是不會哭著跑掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.01,0:13:27.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.14,0:13:30.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.90,0:13:49.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原村同學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.18,0:13:57.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原村同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.03,0:14:10.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原村同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.52,0:14:15.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於我而言  麻將一直都是和家人一起玩的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.69,0:14:19.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後還一直都伴隨著不愉快的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.97,0:14:24.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是勝是負都只會被訓斥的一種儀式
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.63,0:14:27.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是對於我而言的「麻將」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.23,0:14:30.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  今天卻有所不同了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.13,0:14:34.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和原村同學一起打麻將後
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.58,0:14:36.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知怎麼  有了一種很開心的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.09,0:14:40.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼的  贏了自然會高興的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.35,0:14:42.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.21,0:14:46.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為對手是原村同學的緣故
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.78,0:14:52.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有原村同學在  就有了和家裡人打麻將時不同的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.39,0:14:53.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很高難度
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.76,0:14:55.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.29,0:14:59.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.70,0:15:07.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…原村同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.54,0:15:10.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.93,0:15:15.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.06,0:15:18.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡麻將
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.48,0:15:22.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  輸給你讓我感到很不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.41,0:15:29.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是不喜歡麻將的你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.27,0:15:33.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.87,0:15:39.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜歡麻將
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.30,0:15:43.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.67,0:15:45.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.48,0:15:49.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不是我  難纏的對手也有的是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.63,0:15:53.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在全國範圍內…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.34,0:16:03.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全國…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.07,0:16:12.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部長  為什麼站在那種地方擺Pose耍帥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.35,0:16:16.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙  不准對部長說那麼失禮的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.92,0:16:48.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡麻將
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.65,0:16:52.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  輸給你讓我感到很不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.40,0:16:56.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是不喜歡麻將的你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.98,0:17:04.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不喜歡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.14,0:17:09.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咲  很難得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.88,0:17:11.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然會去摸麻將桌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.14,0:17:16.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  不知不覺中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.09,0:17:20.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿這個打一盤嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.41,0:17:21.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.35,0:17:25.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為  已經不會再和家人打麻將了不是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.45,0:17:33.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再一會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.72,0:17:34.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.77,0:17:36.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再放一會兒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.27,0:17:39.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽她們一定還會回家來的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.10,0:17:43.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時候再大家一起打吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.30,0:17:45.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會怎樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.78,0:17:48.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.34,0:17:53.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,57頁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.33,0:19:20.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.69,0:19:23.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.38,0:19:39.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.89,0:20:22.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.68,0:20:24.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.98,0:20:40.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宮永同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.89,0:20:52.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.54,0:20:56.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能讓我加入這裡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.37,0:21:03.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎來到麻將部
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.49,0:21:05.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.78,0:21:06.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.84,0:21:11.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還想再多多地和原村同學對局
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.41,0:21:16.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和原村同學多對幾局  然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.56,0:21:19.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再多贏幾局麻將
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.84,0:21:23.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就坐在那裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.06,0:21:26.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天可不會讓你贏了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.14,0:21:27.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.15,0:21:32.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  那就趕緊開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.47,0:21:33.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那我也來參戰嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.21,0:21:34.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.07,0:21:36.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.23,0:21:40.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就和預想的一樣  是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.13,0:21:43.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.73,0:21:45.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是一點沒變呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.50,0:21:48.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底揣測了多遠的事啊  你這個人真是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.82,0:21:52.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這樣的話  就能向全國進軍了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.31,0:21:54.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.04,0:22:00.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.75,0:22:05.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才剛開始呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,====================================
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.78,0:22:12.37,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,がんばっちゃった　がんばった我々
